This directory contains example programs for using DMbuffers to
capture and playback video to and from memory.

These examples work only on the mvp video device.

vtov
----
Receive video input to a DMbuffer and send the DMbuffer to video output.

vtos
----
Receive video input to a DMbuffer and display it on the graphics screen.

vtom
----
Receive video input to a DMbuffer and save it to a file.

mtov
----
Read video images from a file into DMbuffers and send them to video output.
